data.text:
Welcome to MazdaMiniTruckin' one of the last remaining websites where you will find some incredibly helpful information about the 86-93 Mazda B2000, B2200, and B2600i pickup trucks.

The information you will find here has been gathered from other sources, and stored here just in case those other sources such as forums and blogs disappear.

A lot of the information and how-to documents are member contributed from members of our Facebook group. If you have one of these trucks, join our Facebook group and join the discussions.

Click the Facebook icon above to join.
